sequenceDiagram
    title 時序圖 5/7 — 心跳安全機制
    %% 說明：Cockpit 每秒發送 heartbeat（reliable=false）經 LiveKit DataChannel 至
    %%       Edge Agent 與 R2 Bridge。Edge Agent 每 500ms 檢查心跳新鮮度，
    %%       R2 Bridge watchdog 每 500ms 檢查 3 秒超時。任一方超時即觸發安全模式。
    %% 關鍵：Edge Agent 超時 → 停止 Go Publisher + 進入 safe_mode
    %%       R2 Bridge 超時 → 發布 ROS2 /rvep/emergency_stop (Twist zero)

    participant O as "操作員\nOperator"
    participant CP as "Web Cockpit\n(Next.js 3011)"
    participant LK as "LiveKit SFU\n(v1.7.2)"
    participant EA as "Edge Agent\n(TypeScript)"
    participant R2 as "R2 Bridge\n(Python ROS2)"

    Note over CP,R2: 正常持續運作
    loop 每秒 (setInterval 1000ms)
        CP->>CP: ControlChannel.startHeartbeat()
        CP->>LK: DataChannel publishData({type:"heartbeat"}, reliable=false)
        LK-->>EA: Heartbeat Message
        EA->>EA: handleCommand("heartbeat") → reset lastHeartbeatAt
        LK-->>R2: Heartbeat Message
        R2->>R2: watchdog.beat() → reset 3s timer
    end

    Note over EA: Agent Heartbeat Watcher (每 500ms 檢查)
    Note over R2: Watchdog (每 500ms 檢查)
